ADJUST copy_id copy_query
REPLY QR NOERROR
SECTION QUESTION
example.com. IN A
SECTION AUTHORITY
example.com.	IN NS	ns.example.com.
SECTION ADDITIONAL
ns.example.com.		IN 	A	1.2.3.4
