www.example.com. IN A
SECTION ANSWER
www.example.com. 3600 IN A	10.20.30.40
SECTION AUTHORITY
example.com.	3600 IN NS	ns.example.com.
SECTION ADDITIONAL
ns.example.com.	3600 	IN 	A	1.2.3.4
